Important note: MSTest doesn't have `Assert.StartsWith`/`Assert.EndsWith` as instance methods you call on the result. The correct modern MSTest signatures are:

```csharp
Assert.StartsWith("expectedPrefix", actualString);
Assert.EndsWith("expectedSuffix", actualString);
